{"tid":1849888,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"疾控中心：建議民眾獨處時、無特別密切接觸的情況下，可以不用佩戴口罩，亦不必戴一次換一次。","createTime":"2020-01-29T09:36:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-29T10:15:22.000Z","uid":28435,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b6d11767c13e3e3745b782a5c6fbd2f097089ada","tid":1849888,"uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T09:36:25.000Z","msg":"內地新型冠狀病毒肺炎確診個案增至大約6千宗，超越2003年內地沙士個案總數，西藏亦首次出現懷疑病例。<br />\n<br />\n中國疾控中心副主任馮子健說，嬰幼兒確診數量有增加跡象，但重症仍然以中老年人為主，病毒主要透過近距離飛沫傳播，建議民眾到公共場所、乘坐交通工具時戴口罩，但如果獨處、自己駕車或散步、無特別密切接觸的情況下，可以不用佩戴，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>公眾亦不必戴一次換一次。</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n馮子健提到，為了降低春運潮可能帶來的風險，各地部門及專業機構做了大量準備工作，國家衛健委亦印發通知及技術指南，強化指導防控工作。<br />\n<br />\n全民無口罩用既日子來了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"129abfe947967cf90f76b5abfa2b7a91dc1f2e38","tid":1849888,"uid":264871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T09:42:14.000Z","msg":"唔係唔信cdc，美國人病左會隔離自己，啲大陸人係會四圍播毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c64003e9703b9b64661f2ea2d3b008fef5d890d2","tid":1849888,"uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"129abfe947967cf90f76b5abfa2b7a91dc1f2e38","tid":1849888,"uid":264871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T09:42:14.000Z","msg":"唔係唔信cdc，美國人病左會隔離自己，啲大陸人係會四圍播毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T10:03:15.000Z","msg":"為無口罩打定底，好快口罩會唔夠用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"